<div class="com-share" data-id="22020" data-title="《「日本語」日式恐怖片的巅峰期还会来吗》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22020/medium/22020.jpg?1454654016" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22020.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
